[[1982年大西洋飓风季|1982年大西洋飓风季]]是一次活跃度很低的[[大西洋飓风季|大西洋飓风季]]，一共只形成了5场获得命名的[[热带气旋|热带气旋]]<ref name="allBT">{{cite web | author = National Hurricane Center | title = All Tropical Cyclone Tracks for the Atlantic and Eastern Pacific | year = 2008 | publisher = Hydrometeorological Prediction Center | accessdate = 2014-09-22 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20111027081946/http://www.erh.noaa.gov/er/hq/ssd/erps/tm/tm100.pdf | deadurl = no | url = http://www.erh.noaa.gov/er/hq/ssd/erps/tm/tm100.pdf | archivedate = 2011-10-27 | format = [[PDF|PDF]] }}</ref>。飓风季从1982年6月1日正式开始，同年11月30日结束，传统上这样的日期界定了一年中绝大多数[[热带气旋|热带气旋]]在[[大西洋|大西洋盆地]]形成和发展的时间段<ref name = "AOML FAQ G1">{{cite book | url = http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/hrd/tcfaq/tcfaqHED.html | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140601034216/http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/hrd/tcfaq/G1.html | title = Hurricane Research Division: Frequently Asked Questions | chapter = G: Tropical Cyclone Climatology | archivedate = 2014-06-01 | chapterurl = http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/hrd/tcfaq/tcfaqG.html | at = [http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/hrd/tcfaq/G1.html G1) When is hurricane season ?] | author1 = Chris Landsea | author2 = Neal Dorst (ed.) | publisher = Atlantic Oceanographic and Meteorological Laboratory | date = 2011-06-02 | accessdate = 2014-06-25 }}</ref>。不过从1982年的实际情况看，大部分热带天气活动都局限在9月份。'''1982年大西洋飓风季时间轴'''中记录了全年大西洋所有热带或[[亚热带气旋|亚热带气旋]]形成、增强、减弱、登陆、[[温带气旋|转变成温带气旋]]以及消散的具体信息。还包括实际操作中没有发布的信息，如[[国家飓风中心|美国国家飓风中心]]在风暴过后进行的回顾。包括最大持续风速、位置、距离在内的所有数字都是经四舍五入换算成整数。

全季一共形成了8个热带低气压，其中5个获得命名，2场达到飓风强度，1场成为大型飓风{{#tag:ref|大型飓风指[[最大持续风速|最大持续风速]]达到每小时至少179公里的[[热带气旋|热带气旋]]，在[[萨菲尔-辛普森飓风等级|萨菲尔-辛普森飓风等级]]中可以达到三级或以上<ref name="glo">{{cite report | publisher = National Hurricane Center | date = 2013-03-25 | accessdate = 2014-06-15 | title = Glossary of NHC Terms | archivedate = 2014-06-01 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140601020814/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/aboutgloss.shtml | deadurl = no | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/aboutgloss.shtml }}</ref>。|group="注"}}<ref name="allBT" />。[[1982年飓风阿尔贝托|飓风阿尔贝托]]在[[墨西哥湾|墨西哥湾]]达到飓风强度，但最终并没有登陆，截至[[{{CURRENTYEAR}}年大西洋飓风季|{{CURRENTYEAR}}年]]，这种在墨西哥湾成为飓风却没有登陆的情况只发生过4次。另外3场飓风分别是1969年的飓风劳瑞<ref name="allBT" />，[[1979年大西洋飓风季|1979年]]的飓风亨利<ref name="HenriTCR">{{cite web | author = National Hurricane Center | year = 1979 | title = Hurricane Henri (1979) Preliminary Report Page 1 | accessdate = 2014-09-22 | publisher = National Hurricane Center | archivedate = 2012-10-20 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121020184153/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1979-prelim/henri/prelim01.gif | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1979-prelim/henri/prelim01.gif }}</ref>和1980年的[[1980年飓风珍妮|飓风珍妮]]<ref name="JeanneTCR">{{cite web | author = National Hurricane Center | year = 1980 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1980-prelim/jeanne/prelim01.gif | title = Hurricane Jeanne (1980) Preliminary Report | accessdate = 2014-09-22 | publisher = National Hurricane Center | archivedate = 2012-10-20 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121020184055/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1980-prelim/jeanne/prelim01.gif | deadurl = no }}</ref>。但是，阿尔贝托产生的暴雨引发严重洪灾，夺走了[[古巴|古巴]]23条人命<ref>{{cite web | author = National Hurricane Center | year = 1982 | title = Hurricane Alberto Preliminary Report Page 2 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20090320001120/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1982-prelim/alberto/prelim02.gif | archivedate = 2009-03-20 | deadurl = no | publisher = National Hurricane Center | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1982-prelim/alberto/prelim02.gif | accessdate = 2014-09-22 }}</ref>。[[1982年飓风黛比|飓风黛比]]是本季仅有的大型飓风，在大西洋开发海域上空达到四级飓风强度标准<ref>{{cite web | author = National Hurricane Center | year = 1982 | title = Hurricane Debby Preliminary Report Page 3 | publisher = National Hurricane Center | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1982-prelim/debby/prelim03.gif | deadurl = no | accessdate = 2014-09-22 | archivedate = 2012-10-22 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121022201827/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1982-prelim/debby/prelim03.gif }}</ref>。热带风暴埃内斯托是本季最后一场风暴，于10月2日达到最高强度，略低于飓风标准，然后在次日消散<ref name="ErnestoBT">{{cite web | author = National Hurricane Center | year = 1982 | title = Tropical Storm Ernesto Preliminary Report Page 4 | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2014-09-22 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1982-prelim/ernesto/prelim04.gif | archive-date = 2021-01-14 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210114134633/https://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1982-prelim/ernesto/prelim04.gif | dead-url = no }}</ref>，这时距飓风季正式结束还有58天时间<ref name = "AOML FAQ G1" />。

